Former Jozi and YoTV member Luther 'Crazy Lu' Cohen has died. The news broke on social media on Friday evening, with former Jozi member Da L.E.S sending condolences on social media followed by other industry friends. Tthe child died over an apparent astha attack according to reports. The hip-hop community is gutted and have flooded social media with tributes to Crazy Lu.Da L.E.S said, "Rest in peace brother. Very big condolence goes out to the Cohen family. Terribly sorry we couldn’t connect when you were alive. Life’s short." Crazy Lu has been living in the East Asia country for the past three years.    